3.1 Place the notmuch-indicator on the tab-bar
==============================================

The built-in ‚Äòtab-bar-mode‚Äô provides the ‚Äòtab-bar-format‚Äô option to
display additional information on the tab bar instead of showing it on
each mode line.  Add the ‚Äònotmuch-indicator-tab-bar-format‚Äô to the list,
such as with this arrangement:

     (setq tab-bar-format
           '( tab-bar-format-history
              tab-bar-format-tabs
              tab-bar-separator
              tab-bar-format-add-tab
              tab-bar-format-align-right
              notmuch-indicator-tab-bar-format ; here it is
              tab-bar-separator
              tab-bar-format-global))

   Note that unlike the mode line, the indicator on the tab-line is not
clickable.  This is not something we control.


